"     Deputy Editor",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?33/47/34550/contributors\">",
"     Rosemary B Duda, MD, MPH, FACS",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
